column5: if anyone has some free time tonight, i was planning on hitting either scugog or rice. I know them both really well. i have minnows, hut, heater and spare rods if your interested. ,my buddy backed out and dont want to venture out alone. Pm me or call 905 909 0609. If your in oshawa or along the route from oshawa, i will come get you .
good luck hope someone grabs on to this offer
